<br>
I was asked to handle loot rules. This is after I had to take control of The second group of raiders when Seke had to leave and we had so many people bail.<br>
<br>
There were actually 2 raids going. One for AD and one for CC on Golems.<br>
<br>
I was told what the Loot was in MY raid (CC). I thought that person had announced in ADRAID (contained everyone)<br>
<br>
I am glad that there were actually 2 Wrath of Mithaniels and a Quarterstaff that there was no mistake.<br>
<br>
I lottoed two Wraths of Mithaniel (not knowing one had been ninja'd) and the winners were Cartanish (who won first) and Supermay (who theoretically won 2nd).<br>
<br>
Cartanish went and got his. Supermay then went to corpse and looted the Quarterstaff.<br>
<br>
Supermay barely speaks english. I once asked her to help with Sir Lucan way way way long ago and it was like pulling teeth. After it was done, she then asked, &quot;Guards hate, why?&quot; when it was done, and I felt bad that she couldn't even understand me telling her her faction would be ruined. I still never got the message across about the faction because of language issues <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
I am NOT under the impression that SuperMay ninja'd anything. I believe when she got to the corpse, she saw one item (I guess graphic is the same on the staves) and looted it as she was told (and as she had won the loot roll). I hope people are not going to ruin her reputation over this. I believe that was a mistake.<br>
<br>
